{"tid":1525154,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"唔講咁多 9 月 1 （今日） 機場見！","createTime":"2019-08-31T20:02:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T01:29:12.000Z","uid":120070,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6fabf4b1456051020befd6301d803f38c5001db6","tid":1525154,"uid":120070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T20:02:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2057d1554a31325d684ea34520b46a037a31a9b5","tid":1525154,"uid":52230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T20:03:32.000Z","msg":"拆閘機正確方法：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">八達通、入票口首要</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">閘門次要</span></span><br />\n唔好睇小港豬鐘意比錢嘅決心"},{"pid":"829de929086ec2af8de882f85fabad3d7f49f798","tid":1525154,"uid":120070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T20:03:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一人一Post 洗爆連登時事台 Facebook<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n標題：［901入機場］今日重演721，黑警太子版核爆！唔使講野，入機場哂冷<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n與其死係街頭，不如死係機場<br />\n與其街頭食彈，不如機場食彈<br />\n與其被打爆頭，不如機場爆頭<br />\n與其被打爆眼，不如機場爆眼<br />\n與其黨鐵被打，不如機鐵被打<br />\n臥底鐘意燒街，不如燒機場啦<br />\n<br />\n攬炒機場！塞爆佢，唔使講野！<br />\n901無限期塞爆機場！<br />\n<br />\n見者Copy內容開新Post洗版，唔開Post自己檢討一下良心仲係唔係到！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sXnY1hQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsXnY1hQ.jpg&h=abafa30f&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"eea69653dca5b860523e25bd2ced18d75f3a7059","tid":1525154,"uid":94640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T20:23:00.000Z","msg":"大家入機場真係要小心，要記住我地去機場個目標<br />\n唔好再係機場捉鬼比機會對方<br />\n只要我地同旅行一齊，有鬼佢地又可以點"},{"pid":"5aae4a88126d8f4a753256e9f60fcacd36407273","tid":1525154,"uid":17812,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08